about.summary: Different examples and methods for testing (including different proposals described in Ameijeiras-Alonso et al., 2018 <DOI:10.1007/s11749-018-0611-5>) and exploring (including the mode tree, mode forest and SiZer) the number of modes using nonparametric techniques.

name: r-multimode
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.4' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-multimode
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/multimode_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/multimode/multimode_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 9dea73b28162377dc7b4e3a0b99f0b36f850c5e48472963e562a791397145390

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 3
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('fortran') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_fortran') }}  # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-diptest
    - r-ks
    - r-rootsolve
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-diptest
    - r-ks
    - r-rootsolve

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('multimode')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('multimode')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://arxiv.org/abs/1803.00472/
  license: GPL-3
  summary: Different examples and methods for testing (including different proposals described
    in Ameijeiras-Alonso et al., 2018 <DOI:10.1007/s11749-018-0611-5>) and exploring
    (including the mode tree, mode forest and SiZer) the number of modes using nonparametric
    techniques.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - khughitt
